          <article class="postcard-card">
            <div class="postcard-flip">
              <div class="postcard-face postcard-front front-community">
                <div class="front-copy">
                  <circle cx="118" cy="164" r="26" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.22)" />
                  <circle cx="204" cy="132" r="26" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.22)" />
                  <circle cx="292" cy="182" r="26" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.22)" />
                  <path d="M144 156 L184 142 L268 174" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.26)" stroke-width="10" stroke-linecap="round" />
                  <path d="M96 210 C142 244, 208 246, 312 214" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.16)" stroke-width="14" stroke-linecap="round" />
                </svg></div>
              </div>
              <div class="postcard-face postcard-back">
                <div>
                  <span class="mini">Back of card</span>
                  <p>The social map: Discord, Discussions, repo chatter, official forums, and which docks are worth visiting first.</p>
                  <div class="rule"></div>
                  <p><strong>Best if you’re asking:</strong> “Where do these people talk?”</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/community-currents/">Follow the currents →</a>
